  <onto:hasStewardshipDescription rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Keep track of any unusual symptoms such as breathing difficulties, chest pain, cough, or numbness and tingling in the hands or feet. Report these promptly to a healthcare provider to prevent serious complicaions.</onto:hasStewardshipDescription>
</onto:TherapeuticUseAndMonitoring>

