  <onto:hasManagementAdvice rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Consideration should be given to the frequency of monitoring prothrombin time when azithromycin is used in patients receiving coumarin-type oral anticoagulants</onto:hasManagementAdvice>
