  <onto:hasWarningText rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Dose selection for an elderly patient should be cautious, usually starting at the low end of the dosing range, reflecting the greater frequency of decreased hepatic, renal, or cardiac function, and of concomitant disease or other drug therapy.</onto:hasWarningText>
